description:
Costa Chica, in the Mexican state of Oaxaca, is becoming a beach destination thanks to its incredible surfing, eccentric design, and tranquil atmosphere. Videographer César Rodríguez captures some of the beauty of this increasingly popular coastal gem and the unique aesthetic that sets it apart.
